"or <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> Start or stop a game"
msgstr ""
"ou <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> para iniciar ou parar um jogo."

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "A button to change the theme"
